# Environment Variables for Self-Service Form

# Resend API Key (for sending contract emails)
# Get from: https://resend.com/api-keys
RESEND_API_KEY=re_your_api_key_here

# Stripe Secret Key (for payment links)
# Get from: https://dashboard.stripe.com/apikeys
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_your_secret_key_here

# Note: Add these to your Webflow Cloud environment variables:
# 1. Go to Webflow Cloud dashboard
# 2. Navigate to your site settings
# 3. Go to Environment Variables
# 4. Add both RESEND_API_KEY and STRIPE_SECRET_KEY
